OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,FThe SNP will commit to a three-stage
OL,7,Fplan to make the NHS fit for the
OL,8,Ffuture, John Swinney will say as he
OL,9,Flaunches the party's manifesto.
OL,11,FThe First Minister will tell an
OL,12,Faudience in Glasgow that he will offer
OL,13,Fvoters "experienced and trusted
OL,14,Fleadership" that can steer Scotland
OL,15,Fthrough "tough days".
OL,17,FThe SNP leader will also set out "real
OL,18,Faction" to support Scots through the
OL,19,Fcost-of-living crisis.
OL,26,@uD@HOUvD@KO]wD@IOUwD@TO]yD@bOUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
