CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776315855
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,FIn a speech on Thursday, Mr Swinney
OL,7,Fwill unveil his plan to ensure
OL,8,FScotland's NHS is fit for purpose.
OL,10,FHe will set out a three-pronged
OL,11,Fapproach: investment, protection and
OL,12,Frenewal.
OL,14,FThe First Minister will promise that
OL,15,Fthe NHS will get the cash that it
OL,16,Fneeds to cut waiting lists.
OL,18,FHe will promise to protect the health
OL,19,Fservice's founding principles of being
OL,20,Ffree at the point of use.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776315855
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,FAnd he will set out reform to refocus
OL,7,Fresources on keeping people out of
OL,8,Fhospital, while shifting the balance
OL,9,Fof care into the community.
OL,11,FHe is expected to say: "The NHS is our
OL,12,Fmost important public service. We have
OL,13,Fa plan to make our NHS fit for the
OL,14,Ffuture ` with three parts. Investment,
OL,15,Fprotection and renewal.
OL,17,F"Investment that will see the NHS get
OL,18,Fthe resources it needs to deliver
OL,19,Fprogress and keep cutting waiting
OL,20,Ftimes.
OL,26,@sD@XOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
