OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776315855
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,F"Protection of the NHS principles of
OL,7,Fcomprehensive, universal and free at
OL,8,Fthe point of need.
OL,10,F"And mark my words ` never selling
OL,11,Fpatient data to dodgy billionaires and
OL,12,Fthe Palantirs of this world.
OL,14,F"And renewal ` changing how the NHS
OL,15,Fworks, refocusing resources on keeping
OL,16,Fpeople out of hospital, shifting the
OL,17,Fbalance of care.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
