PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776315855
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,F"And, of course, action to the end the
OL,7,F8am rush for GP appointments, as we
OL,8,Fcontinue to roll out GP walk-in
OL,9,Fclinics.
OL,11,F"That is a government focused on
OL,12,Fimproving Scotland's NHS. That is what
OL,13,Fyou get when you vote SNP on May 7."
OL,15,FMr Swinney will urge voters to back
OL,16,Fthe SNP, saying that he offers
OL,17,F"experienced and trusted leadership to
OL,18,Fhelp Scotland through these tough
OL,19,Fdays".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@dO]yD@AOU{D@EO]
