OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776315855
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,FHe will promise to lead a government
OL,7,F"that will always be on Scotland's
OL,8,Fside" and use "all of my energy to
OL,9,Fimprove the lives of the people of
OL,10,FScotland" and "give Scotland, with
OL,11,Findependence, the fresh start our
OL,12,Fcountry needs".
OL,14,FHe will add: "In this election, I am
OL,15,Fasking people to give me the mandate
OL,16,Fto act always with, and for, the
OL,17,Fpeople who live here.
OL,19,F"When I became First Minister, I
OL,20,Fpromised to serve all of the people of
OL,21,FScotland.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@EO]pD@OOUrD@IO]rD@OOUtD@NO]vD@
OL,26,ANOU{D@AOU
