PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776315855
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,F"I reaffirm that promise today and
OL,7,Fcommit to creating the best future I
OL,8,Fcan for our country."
OL,10,FJackie Baillie, deputy leader of
OL,11,FScottish Labour and the party's health
OL,12,Fspokesperson, said Mr Swinney's "brass
OL,13,Fneck" was "absolutely astonishing".
OL,15,FShe said the SNP's record on health
OL,16,Fafter 19 years was "utterly abysmal".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@UO]tD@aOUuD@EO]uD@KOUuD@bO]xD@
