OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776315855
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,FShe added: "SNP ministers engaged in
OL,7,Fcovering up the deaths of patients,
OL,8,Fincluding children at the QEUH due to
OL,9,Fhospital-linked infections, patients
OL,10,Fare being forced to suffer agonising
OL,11,Fwaits in A&E, and our hardworking
OL,12,Fstaff are being pushed to breaking
OL,13,Fpoint.
OL,15,F"If John Swinney and the SNP cared
OL,16,Fwhatsoever about our NHS, they would
OL,17,Fhave bolstered their support for it
OL,18,Flong before now. Instead, as usual,
OL,19,Fthey are choosing to push a grievance
OL,20,Fnarrative to hide their failings. It
OL,21,Fis pathetic."
OL,26,@nD@LOUwD@AOU}D@MO]
