OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,FScottish Conservative deputy leader
OL,7,FRachael Hamilton said iIf the SNP had
OL,8,Fa plan to fix our NHS, "we'd have seen
OL,9,Fit after nearly two disastrous decades
OL,10,Fin power".
OL,12,FShe said: "The nationalists have run
OL,13,Four health service into the ground `
OL,14,Fand John Swinney's been at the top
OL,15,Ftable the whole time. His fingerprints
OL,16,Fare all over the SNP's record of
OL,17,Ffailure.
OL,26,@pD@XOUrD@IO]tD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
