PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776315855
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,F"Swinney has the brass neck to claim
OL,7,Fhe's serving all the people of
OL,8,FScotland ` when he's relentlessly
OL,9,Fpushing for a divisive independence
OL,10,Freferendum that most people don't want.
OL,12,F"The only thing he cares about is
OL,13,Fbreaking up the United Kingdom and if
OL,14,Fhis party get a majority at May's
OL,15,Felection, he will not let up.
OL,17,F"That's why it's critical that pro-UK
OL,18,Fvoters use their peach ballot to vote
OL,19,Ffor the Scottish Conservatives ` it's
OL,20,Fthe tried and tested way to stop an
OL,21,FSNP majority."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@NO]
