OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776315855
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,FScottish Liberal Democrat MP and
OL,7,Felection campaign chair Wendy
OL,8,FChamberlain said: "From Salmond to
OL,9,FSwinney, the SNP have created a
OL,10,Fculture of secrecy and broken promises
OL,11,Fwhich has had a highly damaging impact
OL,12,Fon the level of public trust.
OL,14,F"From questions of financial
OL,15,Fmismanagement to the failure to hold
OL,16,Fpeople like Jordan Linden to account
OL,17,Ffor unacceptable behaviour, it would
OL,18,Fseem that there is something
OL,19,Ffundamentally rotten at the core of
OL,20,Fthe SNP.
OL,26,@pD@SOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
