OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776315855
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,F"Scots are still waiting for promises
OL,7,Fon recruitment in our schools and
OL,8,Fincome tax to be fulfilled and to be
OL,9,Fable to access the NHS via an app,
OL,10,Flike people in England can.
OL,12,F"Swinney and Sturgeon deleted their
OL,13,FCovid WhatsApp messages. The ferry
OL,14,Fnetwork is a mess and pledges on
OL,15,Feducational attainment have been
OL,16,Fdropped.
OL,18,F"No-one will believe a word that their
OL,19,Fmanifesto says.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
