PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776315855
OL,3,CSwinney to launch SNP manifesto with
OL,4,Cplan to make 'NHS fit for the future'
OL,6,F"At the election, Scots can use their
OL,7,Fsecond peach regional ballot paper to
OL,8,Frepair the damage the SNP has caused
OL,9,Fby backing the Scottish Liberal
OL,10,FDemocrats who are committed to
OL,11,Ftransparency, accountability, and to
OL,12,Fchange with fairness at its heart."
